title: Ep.32: NBA Playoffs, Giveaways, World Cup, Old Stories, and Much More!
description: The NBA playoffs are here! We predict the winner of each series, let us know who you think is going all the way. The summer is coming up fast, stay tuned for the official date and time for our one on one's where you can earn some money! We also talk about the World Cup even though we know only what we've learned from Fifa... We take a look back into our high school days and tell hilarious stories.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
